    <h1>Validation Utils Changelog</h1>

    <div class="changelog-entry">
      <h3>
        <span class="security">Security Enhancement</span> - <span class="date">Current Date</span>
      </h3>
      <p><strong>Enhanced URL validation to prevent XSS attacks</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Expanded the check for dangerous URL protocols beyond just <code>javascript:</code></li>
        <li>
          Added checks for additional potentially dangerous protocols including <code>data:</code>,
          <code>vbscript:</code>, <code>file:</code>, <code>about:</code>, <code>blob:</code>, and
          others
        </li>
        <li>
          Improved code organization by using an array of dangerous protocols for better
          maintainability
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        This change significantly improves security by preventing various protocol-based XSS attack
        vectors that could be exploited through URL inputs.
      </p>
    </div>
